description:
PA polls: Dr. Oz-Fetterman tied, Mastriano within striking distance. Biden says Fetterman's wife will be a "great lady in the Senate." Dr. Oz on Pennsylvania's fentanyl problem. Clay's wife on his dad jokes. Kari Lake, GOP candidate for governor of Arizona, joins Clay and Buck to explain how she's turned the tables on the biased media, how she'll push back on unelected bureaucrats if she wins. As is often the case, Biden can't get off the stage in PA. Best movie sequels.
